      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl mb-4">Where he started</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed mb-5">Gabriel was launching his landscaping business from scratch. He had the skills and the drive, but no way to reach new customers. No materials to hand out, no social presence, no strategy for how to introduce himself.</p>
      <p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed mb-8">The goal was to start generating contacts fast, with minimal investment, while the business was still taking shape.</p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl mb-4">What we did</h2>
      <ul class="checklist mb-8">
        <li><strong><a href="/en/services/print-materials-treasure-coast/" style="color:var(--primary)">Professional business cards</a></strong> — clean design with his name, phone number, service, and service area. A tangible tool he can leave at every job and every conversation.</li>
        <li><strong>Brand awareness campaign on <a href="/en/services/facebook-instagram-ads-treasure-coast/" style="color:var(--primary)">Facebook Ads</a></strong> — brand awareness campaign with a $20 initial investment, targeted to homeowners in his service area.</li>
      </ul>

